When the app is lunched, the user would see the app title.

In Menu 3 Options

"1. View departures"
"2. View arrivals"
"3. View clock"

Now the user can type a number.

if 1 is chosen, new options would display.

"Select station:"

1. Waterloo
2. Euston

Again the user can pick an option.

Example: Selects 1
Example: "T-101 leaves at 08:00. Arrives at Euston Station at 08:45."

The same concept would be utilised for the arrivals option

"Select station:"

1. Waterloo
2. Euston

User picks one option.

Example: Selects 2
Example: "T-101 — from Waterloo Station — arrived at 08:45"

or if there are no arrivals 
Example: "No arrivals at this time."
